Name: XOMBEE MPFPS
About the game: XOMBEE MPFPS is a Solo Project made using Unreal Engine 4.26 A FPS played Solo or Online Multiplayer with 3rd Person view added in The Game is Mutant vs Humans with some Maps also containing XOMBEE's to fight as well . 7 Unique Levels to play Maps included are : Conquest , Rush , Vehicle , Team Death Match , Death Match , Capture the Flag , Kill Confirmed 4 Character Classes - Assault , Medic , Support , Scout Some of Weapons included are : Shotgun , Assault Rifle , Sniper Rifle , LMG , 9 mm , Grenades and more ... Some of the Perks included are - Jet Pack , Med Bot , Speed Boost , Mine and more ..... Up to 32 Players and/or Ai Bots 8 Different Soldiers on 2 Teams Alpha Team includes 1-Robot Girl and 3-Male Tech Soldiers Beta Team includes 4 - Mutants With Regular Updates Planned ......................... Thanks for Playing !!!
